      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through its high-pressure double VANOS system and six individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing Bilstein dampers. This is a true driver\u2019s car with zero mechanical lash, offering the telepathic steering response and high-revving induction note that defined an era.",
