      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe the condition of this beauty. I've babied this car since day one, and it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s absolutely spotless inside and out\u2014seriously, not a single scratch or ding to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and has been tucked away in a climate-controlled garage its whole life. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
